e objects in the world to escape your fate as you make your way through the mind-bending halls of The Cecil. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/f24b0b02799a58f98e3f6b39097e3db1.poster.avif?t=1768516713\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/f24b0b02799a58f98e3f6b39097e3db1.webm?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/f24b0b02799a58f98e3f6b39097e3db1.mp4?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Puzzles and Discoveries:</u></strong> Solve fast-paced puzzles and collect discoveries along the way to help you progress to new areas, as you uncover the details of how things came to be at this mysterious hotel.</p>",
